<seg id="1445">Ogg Vorbis library: Ogg Vorbis is a completely open, patent-free, professional audio encoding and streaming technology with all the benefits of Open Source, and in direct competition with the MP3 format. Used by the Ogg Vorbis Decoder and Encoder plugins.</seg>
<seg id="1446">MAD (MPEG Audio Decoder) Library: A high-quality MPEG audio decoder, supporting the MPEG-1, MPEG-2 and MPEG 2.5 formats. All three audio layers Layer I, Layer II, and Layer III (i. e. MP3) are fully implemented. Used by the MP3 Decoder plugin.</seg>
