<seg id="2081">Within & quantaplus; there are several key concepts. To understand and take advantage of & quantaplus;, you must first learn these concepts, the fundamentals. This chapter will explain and show you these concepts, without which & quantaplus; would be primitive.</seg>
<seg id="2082">& quantaplus; divides the workspace into three scopes: Global, Local, and Project. These distinctions affect various components in & quantaplus;.</seg>
